        <prompt>Billy Sunday's role in 1920s American society was as:</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">A prominent evangelist supporting traditional values</option>
            <option letter="b">A political reformer advocating social change</option>
            <option letter="c">A progressive religious leader</option>
